{
  "stem": "18654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 254.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't really remember much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- know it's amazing how little-- I'm always amazed myself how little I remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just remember some incidents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They looked-- I think she looked after us as well as she possibly could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no-- I think what I missed mainly-- I-- I do, I've been told this afterwards by somebody, that I-- I missed-- I must have missed my parents terribly because I mean, a child gets cuddled and kissed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That, of course, didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't know how to-- well, I probably would have rejected it anyway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I do remember an incident that I was told much later in my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I met a man who is a-- a-- a distant cousin of a cousin of mine and he told me that-- that I told him how much I missed this.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I don't honestly remember it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The house that I lived in was a very nice house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was in a very nice area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was sent to an English church school, it was called Holy Trinity Church School in East Finchley.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My sister was far brighter than I was, went to a very good school, and it's a very well-known school in the Hampstead Gardens suburb called Henrietta Barnett School.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I went to this little school where I was very upset because I was put in with the babies because I couldn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And until I learned some English and gradually attained my own class, my age group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember I used to get a penny a day-- not-- not the penny-- not today's penny, the old penny, which I was allowed-- if I was a good girl, which wasn't so often I didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
